yers. If you lose your three balloons, you won't be able to reappear, so play smart to stay in the game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844450/extras/5ab9df301097baf55b75a60bbc67ce2c.poster.avif?t=1767788743\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844450/extras/5ab9df301097baf55b75a60bbc67ce2c.webm?t=1767788743\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844450/extras/5ab9df301097baf55b75a60bbc67ce2c.mp4?t=1767788743\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844450/extras/95503c951517db2c4acadd0f24b0e77d.avif?t=1767788743\" width=600 height=130 /></span><br><br>Unlock a multitude of costumes as you progress with your character, gaining levels and unlocking new appearances for ultimate customization.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844450/extras/163e56a3424e07ddbd8ab40daea36bec.avif?t=1767788743\" width=600 height=540 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844450/extras/f6c8d92ddb5e3ecf8add67bc4bdb7084.avif?t=1767788743\" width=600 height=130 /></span>",
